# Bats test fixtures — generated during test runs, not checked in.
# Exclude the contents of fixtures/ but allow the directory to exist, then
# re-include specific source-of-truth subdirs.
tests/fixtures/*
# Exception: ai-smell-phrases is a source-of-truth phrase list consumed by
# bats linter helpers AND cited in rules/common/output-discipline-voice.md.
# Hand-edited, checked in.
!tests/fixtures/ai-smell-phrases/
